items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: +38% to Chaos Resistance while affected by Purity of Elements
Effects of Consecrated Ground you create while affected by Zealotry Linger for 2 seconds
Gain 9% of Maximum Mana as Extra Maximum Energy Shield while affected by Clarity
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
